in the last election,

00:31:33.710 --> 00:31:36.350
and hopefully it'll be
higher in the next election.

00:31:36.350 --> 00:31:38.880
But, in fact, there was a large drop

00:31:38.880 --> 00:31:43.513
in turnout over the period, '64-2000,

00:31:43.513 --> 00:31:46.280
and the drop was really big among

00:31:46.280 --> 00:31:48.890
less educated people
and lower paid people.

00:31:48.890 --> 00:31:53.560
So today, we have a more unevenly,

00:31:53.560 --> 00:31:56.240
inequality in voting has increased.

00:31:56.240 --> 00:31:59.820
