we could do about it,

00:32:12.060 --> 00:32:14.189
and I think some, many of the states

00:32:14.189 --> 00:32:17.640
are trying to do things, I
think it's been a fair effort

00:32:17.640 --> 00:32:20.410
by many of our states, but right now,

00:32:20.410 --> 00:32:22.187
the voting has shifted from what it was

00:32:22.187 --> 00:32:26.750
in the 1960s, so more and
more, disproportionately,

00:32:26.750 --> 00:32:30.410
the number of the voters,
tend to be higher educated,

