00:38:41.157 --> 00:38:43.427
"on the professorial, we'll
just go off and hire some

00:38:43.427 --> 00:38:47.267
"mathematical economist, and
we'll just shift the resources,

00:38:47.267 --> 00:38:49.710
"so you can't ever let them give you."

