00:55:39.740 --> 00:55:42.310
during this transition, as the technology

00:55:42.310 --> 00:55:45.210
and education is growing up elsewhere,

00:55:45.210 --> 00:55:47.850
we don't wanna take big losses.

00:55:47.850 --> 00:55:49.780
But to our people, so we'd
like to be able to say

00:55:49.780 --> 00:55:51.350
we can do some good things here

00:55:51.350 --> 00:55:53.160
and that'll keep some good industries

00:55:53.160 --> 00:55:57.450
and good jobs here, and I just don't know,

00:55:57.450 --> 00:55:59.010
how, we don't have good evidence

00:55:59.010 --> 00:56:01.695
on how much we can do with that.

00:56:01.695 --> 00:56:05.378
And then I said, well,
there are these dangers.

00:56:05.378 --> 00:56:08.265
I won't ask you to
identify the two people,

00:56:08.265 --> 00:56:11.530
except neither of them is President Bush

00:56:11.530 --> 00:56:15.375
nor Dick Cheney dressed up for Halloween.

00:56:15.375 --> 00:56:18.673
We can have all these
disasters in this period,

00:56:19.510 --> 00:56:22.823
and then I do have a
statement for you here,

00:56:27.370 --> 00:56:28.380
this does come from the administration,

00:56:28.380 --> 00:56:30.343
that I'm obviously very dubious about,

00:56:31.200 --> 00:56:33.839
and they're still looking for the WMDs,

00:56:33.839 --> 00:56:37.727
and then, I wonder what Rumney found.

00:56:37.727 --> 00:56:42.530
Oh my god, so we now
know where the WMDs are,

00:56:42.530 --> 00:56:47.304
and who the enemy of
the country really is.

00:56:47.304 --> 00:56:50.700
But I think, let me phrase it this way,

00:56:50.700 --> 00:56:53.333
'cause I'm no Greek, I mean,

00:56:54.370 --> 00:56:56.586
the administration is what it is,

00:56:56.586 --> 00:56:59.959
and it is though, through
education, research

00:56:59.959 --> 00:57:03.450
and things like that that
we're gonna cure our problems,

00:57:03.450 --> 00:57:05.880
not through other strange things.

00:57:05.880 --> 00:57:09.350
So I am a very positive person at the end,

00:57:09.350 --> 00:57:12.227
I say, "Well, I think we
can overcome this challenge

00:57:12.227 --> 00:57:15.767
"to our democracy, part of
it is that the millionaires

00:57:15.767 --> 00:57:17.457
"and billionaires are not evil people,

00:57:17.457 --> 00:57:20.207
"there's a lot more cooperation

00:57:20.207 --> 00:57:24.070
"than we anticipate from economic models."

00:57:24.070 --> 00:57:26.970
We now have brain scans that show

00:57:26.970 --> 00:57:29.270
this, it's hard wired fairness into us,

00:57:29.270 --> 00:57:30.710
so as people, I don't think we're,

00:57:30.710 --> 00:57:33.520
we're not there to be totally bad,

00:57:33.520 --> 00:57:35.490
and I loved it when Warren Buffett

00:57:35.490 --> 00:57:37.693
