00:57:50.400 --> 00:57:52.300
And it is true, that Mr. Buffett

00:57:52.300 --> 00:57:55.060
for all his being a great millionaire,

00:57:55.060 --> 00:57:58.810
he didn't say these things
while he was making his money.

00:57:58.810 --> 00:58:00.800
He waited till retirement.

00:58:00.800 --> 00:58:04.320
That also says maybe that's
people should respect elders,

00:58:04.320 --> 00:58:06.600
that they have a different perspective.

